CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 10, 1958, pg. 14, reads: "Fellowship Principals - Among those who shared responsibility for the success of the Council of Churchwomen's May Fellowship Day at East Liberty Presbyterian Church, May 2, were, top row, left to right: Mrs. G. A. Orr Jr., Roland Sawyer, group leader; Mrs. E. F. Moyer and Mrs. Marion Johnson, group leader... - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Mrs. G. A. Orr Jr., Roland Sawyer, E. F. Moyer, and Marion Johnson, posed in East Liberty Presbyterian Church
